Package edu.mines.jtk.awt

Components for use with the standard Java AWT and Swing packages.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColorMapListener
    A color map listener listens for changes to a color map.
    ColorMapped
    A color mapped object has a colormap.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorMap
    A color map converts a range of double values to colors.
    FloatColorMap
    Maps arrays of floats to colors.
    Mode
    An abstract mode of interaction.
    ModeManager
    A manager for a set of modes and components.
    ModeMenuItem
    A menu item for a mode.
    ModeToggleButton
    A toggle button for a mode.
